### 01. 최상위 업무 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "테스트 업무",
  "description": "업무 설명입니다.",
  "status": "TODO",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "assigneePublicId": "{{assigneePublicId}}",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-31"
}

### 02. 하위 업무 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "하위 업무",
  "description": "하위 업무 설명입니다.",
  "status": "TODO",
  "priority": "MEDIUM",
  "assigneePublicId": "{{assigneePublicId}}",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-15",
  "parentTaskPublicId": "{{parentTaskPublicId}}"
}

### 03. 업무 목록 조회 (페이지네이션)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks?page=0&size=20&sort=dueDate,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 04. 업무 목록 조회 (상태 + 우선순위 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks?status=TODO&priority=HIGH&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 05. 업무 목록 조회 (마감일 범위 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks?dueDateFrom=2026-05-01&dueDateTo=2026-05-31&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 06. 업무 목록 조회 (담당자 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks?assigneePublicId={{assigneePublicId}}&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 07. 업무 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 08. 업무 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "수정된 업무명",
  "description": "수정된 설명",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "priority": "URGENT",
  "assigneePublicId": "{{assigneePublicId}}",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-15"
}
